body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, thank you for contacting us today. My name is Logan Gonzales and I represent SafeRide Car Dealership. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Jessica. How can I assist you today? Before we proceed, may I kindly ask for the last four digits of your phone number, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My phone number ends in two three four five.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Jessica. Can you also provide me with the month and day of your birthdate, please?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My birthdate is in March, on the second.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Great, thank you for sharing that information, Jessica. Is there anything else you would like to discuss today?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm feeling confused about the privacy policy. Can you explain it to me?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Of course! I'll help clarify that for you, Jessica. Thank you for bringing it up. Is there anything specific you are unsure about?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: I'm not sure about how my personal data is being used.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I understand, Jessica. Your privacy is important to us, and I will explain how we handle your data. Thank you for your time and for reaching out to us today. If you have any further questions, don't hesitate to ask.
